Callaghan stood up Military Sea Transportation Service (MSTS) at the Main Navy and Munitions Building, Washington DC. We will honor our historical significance within the maritime environment, the versatility and capability of our fleet and the contributions and sacrifices made by our Civil Service Mariners – past and present – along with the Sailors and civilian employees who support them through numerous public affairs products; community outreach; special observances and special events.
